ervice%20of%20summons%20or%20arrest%20warrant%20is%20part%20of%20mutual%20legal%20assistance%2C%20but%20such%20requests%20are%20examined%20on%20merits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20received%20any%20request%20on%20this%20case%20from%20the%20US%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20asserted.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20matter%20which%20pertains%20to%20a%20private%20individual%20and%20private%20entities.%20The%20government%20of%20India%20is%20not%20a%20part%20of%20it%20in%20any%20manner%20at%20this%20point%20in%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20Chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20his%20nephew%20Sagar%20Adani%2C%20and%20senior%20executive%20Vneet%20Jaain%20are%20clear%20of%20any%20bribery%20charges%20per%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Green%2C%20a%20firm%20under%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20had%20also%20called%20media%20reports%20on%20the%20US%20legal%20matter%20as%20%26quot%3Bincorrect%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20a%20stock%20exchange%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Mr%20Sagar%20Adani%20and%20Mr%20Vneet%20Jaain%20have%20not%20been%20charged%20with%20any%20violation%20of%20the%20FCPA%20in%20the%20counts%20set%20forth%20in%20the%20indictment%20of%20the%20US%20DOJ%20or%20civil%20complaint%20of%20the%20US%20SEC%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Adani%20Group%20said%20in%20the%20statement%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20US%20Foreign%20Corruption%20Practices%20Act%20(FCPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20includes%20five%20counts%2C%20but%20the%20first%20and%20fifth%20counts%20-%20conspiracy%20to%20violate%20the%20FCPA%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20obstruct%20justice%20-%20do%20not%20mention%20the%20three%20directors%2C%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Sagar%20Adani%2C%20and%20Vneet%20Jaain%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20statement%20said%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bflawed%20understanding%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20US%20indictment%20by%20various%20media%2C%20foreign%20as%20well%20as%20Indian%2C%20has%20led%20to%20%26quot%3Bincorrect%20and%20reckless%20reporting%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20three%20Adani%20Group%20directors%20faced%20corruption%20and%20bribery%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20indictment%20relies%20only%20on%20claims%20that%20bribes%20were%20discussed%20or%20promised.%20It%20did%20not%20offer%20any%20evidence%20that%20Indian%20government%20officials%20received%20bribes%20from%20Adani%20executives%2C%20the%20group%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20lawyer%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%20later%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20there's%20no%20detail%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20about%20who%20has%20been%20bribed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ill-founded%20US%20action%20and%20reckless%20false%20reporting%20have%20led%20to%20significant%20repercussions%20for%20the%20Indian%20conglomerate%2C%20such%20as%20international%20project%20cancellations%2C%20financial%20market%20impact%2C%20and%20sudden%20examination%20from%20strategic%20partners%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Adani%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732882380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fvid7b8cg_adani-group_625x300_27_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-havent-received-any-request-from-us-foreign-ministry-on-adani-case-7133468%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20not%20received%20any%20communication%20from%20the%20US%20on%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20in%20its%20weekly%20briefing%20today%2C%20firmly%20denying%20reports%20of%20summons%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group%20Chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%20