.com%2Fsatellite-images-china-mock-ford-carrier-target-western-desert-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20has%20been%20practicing%20for%20such%20an%20engagement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20November%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-built-us-warship-mock-ups-for-possible-target-practice-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esatellite%20images%20showed%20apparent%20full-scale%20outlines%20of%20US%20Navy%20aircraft%20carriers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Ruoqiang%20area%20of%20Xinjiang's%20Taklamakan%20desert%20in%20northwestern%20China.%20Satellite%20images%20have%20also%20spotted%20mock-ups%20of%20American%20destroyers%20and%20big-deck%20amphibious%20assault%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaval%20power%20is%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20American%20military%20might%2C%20but%20the%20DF-26%20threatens%20that%2C%20among%20various%20other%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22287cf922-0cf2-482f-862b-ea14300df7c7%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20the%20US%20counter%20the%20DF-26%20threat%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222211%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20aircraft%20carrier%20sails%20in%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20with%20a%20cloudy%20sunset%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6688298b1aace5b3ada4c0c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221474%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20Carl%20Vinson%20transits%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean.%3Cp%3ENavy%20Ensign%20Sarah%20Weinstein%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20lawmakers%20have%20raised%20concerns%20with%20the%20Air%20Force%20and%20Navy%20secretaries%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-pacific-bases-aircraft-vulnerable-to-chinese-missiles-lawmakers-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evulnerability%20of%20American%20bases%20in%20the%20Pacific%20to%20Chinese%20missile%20barrages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20officials%20have%20indicated%20a%