s%20now%20worth%20%C2%A383%20million%20and%20owns%20multiple%20houses%20in%20Monte%20Carlo%2C%20a%20yacht%20and%20is%20a%20board%20member%20of%20Bank%20Rossiya%20-%20a%20bank%20used%20by%20the%20elites%20to%20move%20money%20around.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20she%20also%20has%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20Igora%20Ski%20Resort%20near%20Finland%20and%20is%20the%20director%20of%20National%20Media%20Group%2C%20which%20is%20used%20to%20regulate%20key%20propaganda%20channels%20by%20the%20Kremlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaked%20Pandora%20Papers%20brought%20out%20in%20the%20open%20how%20Krivonogikh%20gradually%20became%20rich%20after%202000%20when%20Putin%20became%20Russia's%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProekt%2C%20an%20independent%20investigative%20news%20organisation%2C%20mentions%20that%20Krivonogikh%20and%20Putin%20developed%20a%20friendship%20when%20he%20was%20St%20Petersburg's%20mayor%2C%20while%20also%20being%20married%20to%20Lyudmila%20Shkrebneva%2C%20with%20whom%20he%20has%20two%20legitimate%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERozova%20had%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20on%20which%20she%20posted%20photos%20of%20herself%2C%20posing%20and%20dancing.%20However%2C%20she%20deleted%20her%20accounts%20in%202022%2C%20shortly%20after%20Putin%20announced%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20when%20she%20was%20trolled%20in%20the%20comments%20with%20people%20posting%20Ukraine%20flag%20emojis%20and%20accusing%20her%20of%20hiding%20in%20a%20bunker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20according%20to%20Luiza%20Rozova's%20birth%20certificate%2C%20she%20does%20not%20have%20a%20father's%20name%20but%20her%20patronymic%20name%20has%20been%20mentioned%20as%20Vladimirovna%20but%20Rozova%20denied%20any%20connection%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BListen%2C%20judging%20by%20his%20young%20photos%2C%20probably%2C%20yes%2C%20it%20looks%20similar.%20But%2C%20as%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20look%20like%20Vladimir%20Vladimirovich%26quot%3B%2C%20using%20the%20formal%20address%20in%20Russian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndrey%20Zakharov%2C%20now%20a%20BBC%20journalist%2C%20had%20then%20broken%20the%20story%20for%20Proekt.%20%26quot%3BHave%20I%20caused%20you%20a%20bad%20trauma%20by%20my%20investigation%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20Rozova%20on%20Clubhouse%2C%20a%20social%20audio%20app%2C%20to%20which%20she%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20no%2C%20not%20at%20all.%20My%20life%20was%20so%20stagnant%2C%20I%20am%20very%20grateful%20for%20the%20chance%20to%20be%20in%20the%20limelight%2C%20that%20people%20heard%20about%20my%20account.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732881240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fc8k7k6p8_vladimir-putin-reuters_625x300_29_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvladimir-putins-secret-daughter-hiding-in-paris-since-ukraine-war-report-7134081%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rozova%20had%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20on%20which%20she%20posted%20photos%20of%20herself%2C%20posing%20and%20dancing.%20However%2C%20she%20deleted%20her%20accounts%20in%202022%2C%20shortly%20after%20Putin%20announced%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvladimir-putins-secret-daughter-hiding-in-paris-since-ukraine-war-report-7134081%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20GDP%20Growth%20Slowed%20To%205.4%25%20In%20July-September%2C%20Lowest%20In%202%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20economic%20growth%20slowed%20to%20near%20two-year%20low%20of%205.4%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20July-September%20quarter%20of%20this%20fiscal%20due%20to%20poor%20performance%20of%20manufacturing%20and%20mining%20sectors%2C%20but%20the%20country%20continued%20to%20remain%20the%20fastest-growing%20large%20economy%2C%20data%20showed%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%20had%20expanded%20by%208.1%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20July-September%20quarter%20of%202023-24%20fiscal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20low%20level%20of%20GDP%20growth%20at%204.3%20per%20cent%20was%20recorded%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20(October-December%202022)%20of%20financial%20year%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India%20remained%20the%20fastest-growing%20major%20economy%20as%20China's%20GDP%20growth%20in%20the%20July-September%20quarter%20this%20year%20was%20at%204.6%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20(NSO)%20data%2C%20the%20growth%20of%20agriculture%20sector%20GVA%20(Gross%20Value%20Added)%20accelerated%20to%203.5%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20latest%20July-September%20quarter%20from%201.7%20per%20cent%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GVA%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20slowed%20to%202.2%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20the%20current%20fiscal%20compared%20to%20an%20expansion%20of%2014.3%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20data%2C%20the%20output%20(GVA)%20in%20the%20'mining%20and%20quarrying'%20contracted%20to%200.01%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20against%20a%20growth%20of%2011.1%20per%20cent%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expansion%20in%20financial%2C%20real%20estate%20and%20professional%20services'%20GVA%20was%206.7%20per%20cent%2C%20up%20from%206.2%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20year-ago%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectricity%2C%20gas%2C%20water%20supply%20and%20other%20utility%20services%20grew%20by%203.3%20per%20cent%2C%20slower%20than%2010.5%20per%20cent%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20sector%20recorded%20a%20growth%20of%207.7%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20down%20from%2013.6%20per%20cent%20year%20on%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20growth%20in%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%20during%20the%20April-June%20quarter%20of%202024-25%20remained%20unchanged%20at%206.7%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReal%20GDP%20or%20GDP%20at%20constant%20prices%20in%20Q2%20of%202024-25%20is%20estimated%20at%20Rs%2044.10%20lakh%20crore%2C%20against%20Rs%2041.86%20lakh%20crore%20in%20Q2%20of%202023-24%2C%20showing%20a%20growth%20rate%20of%205.4%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NSO%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENominal%20GDP%20or%20GDP%20at%20current%20prices%20in%20Q2%20of%202024-25%20is%20estimated%20at%20Rs%2076.60%20lakh%20crore%2C%20against%20Rs%2070.90%20lakh%20crore%20in%20Q2%20of%202023-24%2C%20showing%20a%20growth%20rate%20of%208.0%20per%20cent%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20half-yearly%20basis%2C%20the%20statement%20said%20the%20real%20GDP%20or%20GDP%20at%20constant%20prices%20in%20April-September%20of%202024-25%20(H1%20FY25)%20is%20estimated%20at%20Rs%2087.74%20lakh%20crore%2C%20against%20Rs%2082.77%20lakh%20crore%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023-24%2C%20showing%20a%20growth%20rate%20of%206%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENominal%20GDP%20or%20GDP%20at%20current%20prices%20in%20H1%2C%202024-25%20is%20estimated%20at%20Rs%20153.91%20lakh%20crore%2C%20against%20Rs%20141.40%20lakh%20crore%20in%20H1%20of%202023-24%2C%20showing%20a%20growth%20rate%20of%208.9%20per%20cent%2C%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20government%20data%20showed%20that%20the%20Centre's%20fiscal%20deficit%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20seven%20months%20of%20the%20current%20financial%20year%20touched%2046.5%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20full-year%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20absolute%20terms%2C%20the%20fiscal%20deficit%20--%20the%20gap%20between%20government's%20expenditure%20and%20revenue%20--%20was%20at%20Rs%207%2C50%2C824%20crore%20during%20April-October%20period%2C%20according%20to%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Controller%20General%20of%20Accounts%20(CGA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deficit%20stood%20at%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Budget%20Estimates%20(BE)%20i