%20title%3D%5C%22Prithvi%20Shaw%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107533-prithvi-shaw-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPrithvi%20Shaw%3C%2Fa%3E's%20stocks%20hit%20rock%20bottom%20after%20he%20went%20unsold%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20mega%20auction.%20Shaw%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Capitals%20franchise%20since%202018%20but%20was%20released%20ahead%20of%20the%20auction.%20Not%20a%20single%20franchise%20bid%20for%20him%20and%20his%20name%20didn't%20come%20in%20the%20accelerated%20phase%20of%20the%20auction%20either.%20DC%20co-owner%20Parth%20Jindal%2C%20who%20worked%20closely%20with%20Shaw%20in%20the%20past%2C%20has%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20talented%20batter's%20downfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%20scripted%20history%20when%20he%20scored%20a%20ton%20on%20his%20debut%20for%20India.%20His%20early%20days%20in%20international%20cricket%20painted%20quite%20a%20promising%20picture.%20But%2C%20not%20a%20lot%20has%20gone%20right%20for%20him%20since%20then.%20The%20batter%20isn't%20even%20a%20regular%20in%20Mumbai's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20team%20anymore.%20Out%20of%20an%20IPL%20contract%2C%20Shaw%20truly%20has%20his%20back%20against%20the%20wall.%20But%2C%20Jindal%20feels%20that%20is%20a%20good%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrithvi%20is%20a%20great%20kid%2C%20but%20is%20misunderstood%20in%20many%20ways.%20I%20think%2C%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20we%20all%20need%20a%20jolt%2C%20and%20need%20to%20be%20shaken%20up%20from%20our%20slump.%20But%20when%20all%20your%20life%20you%20grow%20up%20hearing%20that%20you%20are%20the%20special%20open%2C%20the%20most%20talented%2C%20and%20is%20the%20only%20other%20batsman%20in%20the%20world%20other%20than%20Sachin%20and%20Kohli%20to%20own%20an%20MRF%20bat%2C%20that%20tells%20you%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomebody%20called%20him%20Lara%2C%20somebody%20called%20him%20Sachin%2C%20or%20the%20next%20big%20thing...so%20grew%20up%20in%20that%20environment.%20Eve