in-person%20meeting%20to%20red-flag%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20serious%20and%20grave%20inconsistencies...%20in%20data%20related%20to%20polling%20and%20counting%20processes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2012-page%20document%20submitted%20this%20afternoon%2C%20the%20Congress%20also%20referred%20to%20doubts%20about%20voter%20data%20that%20were%20raised%20by%20former%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20SY%20Quraishi%20and%20raised%20two%20points%20of%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20was%20%26quot%3Barbitrary%20deletion%20of%20voters.%20and%20subsequent%20addition%20of%20over%2010%2C000%20voters%20in%20each%20constituency%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20second%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Binexplicable%20increase%20in%20voting%20percentages...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20these%20points%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20alleged%20a%20systemic%20effort%20to%20try%20and%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20voters%20(and%20votes)%20%26quot%3Bsympathetic%20to%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Congress%20is%20a%20member%2C%20and%20which%20lost%20heavily%20to%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20combine)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHere%20is%20a%20memorandum%20just%20submitted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FECISVEEP%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ECISVEEP%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20elections%20by%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNANA_PATOLE%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40NANA_PATOLE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMukulWasnik%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MukulWasnik%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Shri%20Ramesh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchennithala%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40chennithala%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThey%20have%20raised%20serious%20issues%20which%20are%20being%20discussed%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20They%20have%20asked%20the%20EC%20for%20an%20in-person%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FK4zfx5tjhF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FK4zfx5tjhF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1862408175322091855%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20urged%20the%20EC%20to%20conduct%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20its%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress'%20Complaints%20To%20EC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20claims%20made%20in%20its%20submission%20to%20the%20EC%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Barbitrary%20inclusion%2Fdeletion%20of%20voter%20records%26quot%3B%20led%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20increase%20of%20(around)%2047%20lakh%20voters%20being%20added%20to%20the%20electoral%20roll%20from%20between%20July%202024%20and%20November%202024%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20significant%20to%20note%20that%20out%20of%20the%2050%20Assembly%20seats%20where%20there%20was%20an%20average%20increase%20of%2050%2C000%20voters%2C%20the%20ruling%20regime%20and%20its%20allies%20secured%20victory%20from%2047...%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20submitted%20alleged%20manipulation%20of%20voter%20list%20at%20the%20Tuljapur%20seat%20as%20an%20example%2C%20noting%20%26quot%3Bfake%20Aadhaar%20cards%20were%20created%20by%20individuals%20with%20differing%20photos%20and%20names%26quot%3B%20to%20cast%20illegal%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tuljapur%20seat%20-%20held%20by%20the%20Congress'%20Madhukarrao%20Chavan%20from%201999%20to%202014%20-%20was%20won%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Ranajagjitsinha%20Patil%20by%2037%2C000%20votes.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20BJP%20has%20ever%20won%20this%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20second%20red-flag%20-%20i.e.%2C%20discrepancies%20in%20voter%20turnout%20data%20-%20the%20Congress%20pointed%20out%20the%20EC's%20average%20voter%20turnout%20at%205%20pm%20was%2058.22%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20that%20this%20jumped%20to%2065.02%20per%20cent%20by%2011.30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20there%20was%20another%20increase%20in%20voting%20percentage%2C%20ultimately%20being%20reported%20as%2066.05%20per%20cent%2C%20several%20hours%20prior%20to%20counting.%20From%20a%20common%20sense%20viewpoint%2C%20over%2070%20lakh%20votes%20being%20cast%20in%20the%20closing%20hour%20of%20polling%20is%20implausible%20and%20unheard%20of%20in%20electoral%20history...%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20reasoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20assuming%20time%20taken%20by%20one%20individual%20to%20cast%20their%20vote%20is%20two%20minutes...%20it%20is%20impossible%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20have%20even%20come%20out%20with%20the%20final%20data%20by%2011.30%20pm%2C%20considering%20that%2076%20lakh%20voters%20would%20have%20exercised%20their%20franchise%20within%20the%20last%20hour%20of%20polling...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20submitted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress'%20letter%20concluded%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat%20the%20said%20discrepancies%20raise%20several%20questions%20about%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20election%20was%20conducted%20across%20Maharashtra.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress'%20Complaints%20About%20Haryana%20Loss%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20claims%20about%20voter%20fraud%2C%20the%20slow%20rate%20at%20which%20data%20is%20published%20(on%20the%20EC's%20website)%20on%20counting%20day%2C%20and%20the%20credibility%20of%20EVMs%2C%20or%20electronic%20voting%20machines%2C%20made%20headlines%20earlier%20this%20month%20too%2C%20after%20the%20Congress%20complained%20about%20the%20Haryana%20poll%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExit%20polls%20had%20expected%20the%20party%20to%20claim%20a%20convincing%20win%20and%20the%20day%20began%20well%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20surging%20into%20an%20early%20big%20lead.%20However%2C%20as%20counting%20continued%20the%20BJP%20scripted%20a%20comeback%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20a%20comfortable%20win%20to%20claim%20a%20historic%20third%20term%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20furious%20Congress%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20verdict%2C%20insisting%20EVMs%20had%20been%20hacked%20and%20raising%20questions%20about%20alleged%20delays%20in%20the%20Election%20Commission%20publishing%20voting%20data%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEC's%20Response%20To%20Earlier%20Congress%20Complaint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20complaints%20about%20the%20Haryana%20result%2C%20the%20EC%20had%20hit%20back%20hard%2C%20criticising%20the%20Congress%20for%20making%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20allegations...%20when%20faced%20with%20inconvenient%20electoral%20outcomes%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20warning%20it%2C%20and%20other%20parties%2C%20against%20%26quot%3Bunfounded%20and%20sensational%20complaints%26quot%3B%20during%20voting%20and%20counting%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FREAD%2520%7C%2520%2522Haryana%2520Electoral%2520Process%2520Flawless%2522%3A%2520EC%2520Hits%2520Back%2520At%2520Congress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BHaryana%20Electoral%20Process%20Flawless%26quot%3B%3A%20EC%20Hits%20Back%20At%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Slams%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20complaints%20about%20EVMs%20and%20potential%20voter%20fraud%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20been%20picked%20up%20and%20trashed%20by%20the%20BJP.%20On%20Thursday%20the%20winning%20party%20pointed%20out%20that%20if%20its%20rival's%20claim%20about%20faulty%20EVMs%20are%20true%2C%20then%20the%20results%20of%20elections%20they%20had%20won%20should%20be%20questioned%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C