20Sambhal%20earlier%20this%20week%20as%20the%20court-ordered%20survey%20of%20the%20mosque%20led%20to%20violent%20clashes%20between%20the%20locals%20and%20the%20police%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20several%20individuals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%2C%20police%20said%2C%20started%20when%20a%20crowd%20gathered%20near%20the%20mosque%20as%20the%20survey%20team%2C%20led%20by%20an%20%26quot%3BAdvocate%20Commissioner%2C%26quot%3B%20began%20its%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsambhal-mosque-jama-masjid-up-violence-16th-century-mosque-a-city-on-fire-sambhal-violence-explained-7100779%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E16th%20Century%20Mosque%2C%20A%20City%20On%20Fire%3A%20Sambhal%20Violence%20Explained%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20swelled%20to%20nearly%20a%20thousand%20people%2C%20and%20they%20tried%20to%20prevent%20the%20police%20from%20entering%20the%20mosque.%20Some%20people%20in%20the%20crowd%20threw%20stones%20at%20the%20police%20personnel%20stationed%20at%20the%20site.%20The%20mob%20also%20set%20ablaze%20more%20than%20ten%20vehicles.%C2%A0The%20police%20responded%20with%20tear%20gas.%20In%20the%20chaos%2C%20several%20were%20killed%20and%20over%2030%20police%20personnel%20were%20injured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20violence%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20announced%20a%20three-member%20judicial%20inquiry%20commission%20to%20investigate%20the%20riots.%20The%20commission%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20within%20two%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20in%20Sambhal%20was%20heightened%20today%20as%20well%20in%20light%20of%20Friday%20prayers%20and%20the%20submission%20of%20the%20ASI%20survey%20report%20to%20the%20trial%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20MP%20from%20Sambhal%2C%20Zia%20Ur%20Rahman%20Barq%2C%20welcomed%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20crucial%20step%20toward%20restoring%20peace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20this%20decision.%20We%20will%20soon%20file%20a%20new%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20demanding%20that%20the%20Sambhal%20incident%20be%20investigated%20by%20a%20commission%20headed%20by%20a%20sitting%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20We%20will%20very%20soon%20file%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Barq%2C%20who%20is%20among%20400%20others%20charged%20over%20the%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBone%20Of%20Contention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20when%20a%20petition%20was%20filed%20in%20Sambhal%20by%20advocate%20Vishnu%20Shanker%20Jain%20and%20others.%20Mr%20Jain%2C%20also%20known%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20and%20Krishna%20Janmabhoomi%20disputes%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20was%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20a%20temple%20dedicated%20to%20Lord%20Kalki.%20The%20petition%20alleged%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20constructed%20after%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20temple%20during%20Babur's%20invasion%20in%201526-27.%20The%20petitioners%20argue%20that%20historical%20texts%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BBaburnamah%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAin-e-Akbari%26quot%3B%20document%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20temple%20by%20Babur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20claims%20that%20the%20temple%20was%20built%20by%20the%20Hindu%20mythological%20figure%20Vishwakarma%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20universe.%20Babur's%20forces%20allegedly%20destroyed%20the%20temple%20partially%20and%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20mosque%20to%20establish%20Islamic%20supremacy.%20The%20petition%20further%20criticises%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20for%20failing%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20site%2C%20as%20it%20is%20a%20protected%20monument%20under%20the%20Ancient%20Monuments%20and%20Archaeological%20Sites%20and%20Remains%20Act%2C%201958.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20demand%20unrestricted%20access%20to%20the%20mosque%20for%20Hindus%2C%20claiming%20their%20right%20to%20worship%20was%20being%20unlawfully%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20court%20ordered%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20mosque%20on%20November%2019%2C%202024.%20Advocate%20Commissioner%20Ramesh%20Raghav%2C%20along%20with%20the%20district%20administration%20and%20police%2C%20carried%20out%20the%20survey%20the%20same%20day.%20This%20rapid%20action%20drew%20criticism%20from%20several%20quarters%2C%20with%20claims%20of%20judicial%20overreach%20and%20procedural%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20community%2C%20including%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20management%20committee%2C%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20survey.%20They%20pointed%20to%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%2C%201991%2C%20which%20prohibits%20altering%20the%20status%20of%20any%20religious%20site%20as%20it%20existed%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947.%20Ziaur%20Rehman%20Barq%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20from%20Sambhal%2C%20condemned%20the%20move%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20disrupt%20communal%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732866000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flrj68o3g_sambhal_625x300_29_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-peace-and-harmony-supreme-court-halts-any-action-on-sambhal-mosque-survey-7132013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sambhal%20Mosque%20Row%3A%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20directed%20the%20management%20committee%20of%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Masjid%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Sambhal%20to%20approach%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20to%20challenge%20the%20trial%20court's%20order.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-peace-and-harmony-supreme-court-halts-any-action-on-sambhal-mosque-survey-7132013%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShe%20Looked%20Happy%20On%20CCTV%2C%20What%20Changed%20In%2015%20Mins%3F%26quot%3B%20Pilot's%20Uncle%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20suicide...%20it%20is%20cold-blooded%2C%20planned%20murder%26quot%3B%20-%20strong%20words%20from%20Vivek%20Tuli%2C%20the%20uncle%20of%2025-year-old%20Srishti%20Tuli%2C%20the%20Air%20India%20pilot%20found%20dead%20at%20her%20Mumbai%20apartment%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrishti%20Tuli%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20lively%20and%20bold%20girl%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20also%20said%2C%20describing%20her%20as%20being%20very%20motivated%20by%20her%20grandfather%2C%20a%20soldier%20who%20died%20for%20his%20country%20in%20the%201971%20war.%20%26quot%3BShe%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20fighter%20pilot%20but%20her%20daadi%20did%20not%20allow%20her%20to%20go%20into%20the%20armed%20forces.%20So%2C%20she%20said%20being%20a%20commercial%20pilot%20is%20also%20wearing%20a%20uniform%20and%20so%20she%20chose%20that%20option.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Tuli's%20uncle%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20to%20protest%20vehemently%20against%20the%20police's%20claim%20his%20niece%20died%20by%20suicide.%20%26quot%3B...%20see%2C%20Srishti%20was%20very%20happy%20at%2011.30%2C%20when%20she%20called%20her%20mother%20and%20said%20everything%20is%20very%20good.%20She%20said%20she%20had%20come%20back%20from%20a%20flight%20and%20had%20to%20fly%20again%20in%20a%20few%20days.%20In%20the%20CCTV%20feed%20also%2C%20which%20police%20showed%20me%2C%20she%20was%20so%20happy%20going%20upstairs%20with%20that%20guy...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20in%2015-20%20minutes%20that%20she%20took%20such%20a%20step%3F%20Can%20it%20happen%3F%20Such%20a%20happy%20girl%20and%2C%20after%2015%20minutes%2C%20she%20is%20no%20more...%20How%20can%20that%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tuli%20thundered%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20commercial%20pilots%20like%20his%20niece%20are%20trained%20to%20cope%20with%20immense%20mental%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20very%20well-trained%20with%20to%20deal%20with%20pressure...%20they%20are%20mentally%20very%20strong.%20How%20can%20they%20be%20afraid%20of%20something%3F%20It%20is%20not%20suicide...%20it%20is%20cold-blooded%2C%20planned%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrishti%20Tuli's%20body%20was%20found%20by%20her%20boyfriend%2C%2027-year-old%20Aditya%20Pandit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20cops%2C%20Ms%20Tuli%20called%20Mr%20Pandit%20-%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Delhi%20by%20road%20-%20early%20Monday%20to%20declare%20she%20would%20die%20by%20suicide.%20Mr%20Pandit%20has%20claimed%20he%20rushed%20back%20but%20found%20the%20door%20of%20Ms%20Tuli's%20flat%20locked.%20Mr%20Pandit%20and%20another%20pilot%2C%20who%20stayed%20in%20the%20same%20building%2C%20called%20a%20locksmith%20and%20forced%20the%20door%20open%2C%20to%20find%20Ms%20Tuli's%20body%20hanging%20from%20the%20ceiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandit%20has%20been%20arrested%20on%20charges%20of%20abetting%20suicide%20after%20complaints%20from%20Ms%20Tuli's%20family%2C%20which%20include%20claims%20he%20was%20extorting%20money.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20managed%20to%20check%20only%20one%20month's%20bank%20statement%20so%20far.%20Around%20Diwali%2C%20about%20Rs%2065%2C000%20was%20transferred%20to%20his%20family%20members.%20I%20am%20convinced%20that%20he%20was%20blackmailing%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tuli%20told%20NDTV%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20this%20morning%2C%20Mr%20Tuli%20also%20questioned%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20-%20which%20included%20a%20fight%20between%20the%20couple%20after%20he%20refused%20to%20stay%20on%20for%20a%20few%20more%20days%20-%20as%20described%20by%20Mr%20Pandit%2C%20that%20led%20up%20to%20Ms%20Tuli's%20body%20being%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20called%20at%202.30...%20police%20told%20me%20she%20had%20a%20video%20call%20with%20Aaditya%20Pandit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20police%20sources%20who%20have%20said%20the%20couple%20had%20a%20video%20call%20moments%20before%20her%20alleged%20suicide.%20%26quot%3BSo%20why%20didn't%20he%20(Mr%20Pandit)%20call%20her%20back%20(after%20he%20received%20Ms%20Tuli's%20call%20warning%20she%20was%20about%20to%20take%20an%20extreme%20step)%20...%20why%20didn't%20he%20call%20his%20friend%20in%20the%20same%20building%20to%20go%20check%20on%20her%3F%20Why%20call%20someone%20living%20three%20kilometres%20away%3F%20Please%20think%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tuli%20also%20said%20he%20had%20full%20faith%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20to%20solve%20this%20crime%2C%20pointing%20out%20progress%20made%20in%20discovering%20that%20Mr%20Pandit%20had%20allegedly%20deleted%20some%20chats%20from%20his%20niece's%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20own%20phone%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20forensic%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732866000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Feeg52rd_air-india-pilot_625x300_28_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-pilot-srishti-tuli-aditya-pandit-she-looked-happy-on-cctv-what-changed-in-15-mins-pilots-uncle-to-ndtv-7132273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20suicide...%20it%20is%20cold-blooded%2C%20planned%20murder%26quot%3B%20-%20strong%20words%20from%20Vivek%20Tuli%2C%20the%20uncle%20of%2025-year-old%20Srishti%20Tuli%2C%20the%20Air%20India%20pilot%20found%20dead%20at%20her%20Mumbai%20apartment%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-pilot-srishti-tuli-aditya-pandit-she-looked-happy-on-cctv-what-changed-in-15-mins-pilots-uncle-to-ndtv-7132273%22%2C%22cd