ion%2C%20focusing%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333727%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-aqi-entrepreneurs-innovations-prevent-stubble-burning-farmers-smog-punjab-haryana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estubble%20burning%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20vehicular%20pollution%2C%20and%20construction%20dust%2C%20but%20coal-burning%20power%20plants%20continue%20to%20operate%20without%20proper%20regulatory%20measures.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20indiscriminate%20blame%20or%20cause%20attributed%20to%20stubble%20burning%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20visible%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20notes%2C%20but%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CStubble%20burning%20only%20pollutes%20for%20two%20or%20three%20weeks%2C%20and%20its%20contribution%20to%20pollution%20throughout%20the%20year%20ranges%20from%200%20to%2030%20percent.%20Of%20course%2C%20it%20is%20a%20major%20contributor%20and%20needs%20to%20stop%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20struggles%20with%20pollution%2C%20looking%20at%20cities%20that%20have%20successfully%20tackled%20the%20issue%20could%20provide%20solutions.%20Barcelona%2C%20which%20has%20greatly%20improved%20its%20air%20quality%2C%20offers%20valuable%20lessons%20for%20Indian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPedestrian-friendly%20%E2%80%98Superblocks%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Europe%E2%80%99s%20most%20polluted%20cities%20throughout%20the%20late%2020th%20century%2C%20Barcelona%20has%20managed%20to%20reduce%20its%20air%20pollution%20with%20the%20help%20of%20progressive%20urban%20planning%2C%20transportation%20reforms%2C%20and%20green%20initiatives.%20In%202019%2C%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20mean%20annual%20PM%20particulate%20matter%20concentration%20was%2017%20%CE%BCg%2Fm%C2%B3%2C%20exceeding%20the%2010%20%CE%BCg%2Fm%C2%B3%20limit.%20Today%2C%20their%20real-time%20PM2.5%20level%20is%206%20%C2%B5g%2Fm%C2%B3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Fla