ocus%20on%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F195571%2Fiit-kharagpur-innovation-deshla-electric-three-wheeler-recharge-home-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs).%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20city%20has%20worked%20hard%20to%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20by%20investing%20in%20EV%20infrastructure%2C%20even%20offering%20incentives%20for%20EV%20owners.%20The%20city%20has%20installed%20over%201%2C000%20charging%20stations%2C%20for%20electric%20cars%20and%20given%20tax%20breaks%20and%20free%20parking%20for%20EV%20owners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20has%20also%20introduced%20electric%20buses%20and%20taxis%20into%20its%20public%20transportation%20network%2C%20further%20reducing%20emissions%20from%20traditional%20fuel-powered%20vehicles.%20This%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%2C%20particularly%20SDG%207%3A%20Affordable%20and%20Clean%20Energy%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20%E2%80%9Censure%20access%20to%20affordable%2C%20reliable%2C%20sustainable%20and%20modern%20energy%20for%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20promote%20cleaner%20transportation%2C%20the%20city%20has%20been%20expanding%20its%20network%20of%20cycling%20and%20pedestrian%20lanes%2C%20with%20over%201%2C000%20kilometres%20of%20these%20pathways%20now%20under%20construction.%20Public%20bike-sharing%20systems%20have%20also%20been%20rolled%20out%20across%20the%20city%2C%20with%20400%20stations%20available%20to%20provide%20easy%20access%20to%20fume-free%20mobility%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommunities%20need%20to%20start%20demanding%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jha.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20demand%20broader%20roads%20and%20better%20flyovers%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20demand%20clean%20air%20from%20our%20political%20