t%20through%20it%20and%20instead%20played%20with%20other%20toddlers%20in%20a%20nearby%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Varijashree%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20concert%2C%20my%20father%2C%20H%20S%20Venugopal%2C%20a%20master%20flautist%2C%20apparently%20heard%20me%20scream%20something.%20Mind%20you%2C%20I%20could%20not%20even%20form%20a%20sentence%20at%20that%20time.%20But%20he%20later%20figured%20out%20that%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20say%20%3Cem%3ERaga%20Hamsadhwani%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20song%20being%20performed%20at%20that%20very%20moment%20was%20in%20%3Cem%3ERaga%20Hamsadhwani%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20home%20from%20the%20concert%2C%20her%20father%20was%20determined%20to%20follow%20up%20on%20what%20had%20just%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20at%20home%2C%20my%20father%20sang%20a%20variety%20of%20classical%20compositions%20from%20different%20composers%2C%20and%20as%20he%20tells%20it%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20form%20and%20structure%20of%20about%2040%20ragas%20(musical%20modes%20in%20Carnatic%20music)%20with%20whatever%20limited%20syllables%20I%20could%20pronounce%20at%20the%20time.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20he%20observed%20early%20on%20that%20I%20had%20a%20%E2%80%98gift%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20such%20incident%20occurred%20when%20Varijashree%20was%20four%20years%20old.%20By%20this%20age%2C%20she%20was%20already%20delivering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F192140%2Fmysore-maharaja-wadiyar-western-classical-music-history-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclassical%20Carnatic%20music%3C%2Fa%3E%20vocal%20performances%20to%20small%20audiences.%20And%20this%20particular%20incident%20took%20place%20during%20one%20of%20her%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20concept%20of%20the%20concert%20was%20that%20I%20would%20sing%20for%20an%20hour.%20Many%20musicians%20attended%20this%20concert%2C%20and%20after%20my%20hour-long%20performance%2C%20they%20sang%20a%20set%20of%20compositions%20in%20100%20different%20%3Cem%3Eragas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20had%20to%20identify%20each%20%3Cem%3Eraga%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20I%20did%20successfully.%20This%20concert%20was%20filmed%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20person%20who%20recorded%20it%20lost%20the%20VHS%20tape.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FIaLqkeKx814%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20her%20beginnings%20as%20a%20child%20prodigy%20in%20Carnatic%20music%20to%20recording%20%E2%80%98A%20Rock%20Somewhere%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20inimitable%20Jacob%20Collier%20and%20Anoushka%20Shankar%20%E2%80%94%20nominated%20this%20year%20for%20a%20Grammy%20Award%20for%20%E2%80%98Best%20Global%20Music%20Performance%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Varijashree%20has%20undertaken%20a%20remarkable%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20musician%20with%20a%20classical%20foundation%20who%20has%20since%20expanded%20into%20diverse%20cross-cultural%20and%20interdisciplinary%20styles%2C%20this%20Grammy%20nomination%20feels%20like%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20not%20just%20this%20song%20but%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316118%2Fbengaluru-interactive-indian-music-experience-museum-bollywood-songs-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emusical%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20have%20undertaken%20so%20far.%20It%20is%20a%20milestone%20that%20reassures%20me%20that%20the%20direction%20I%20am%20taking%20%5Bcreatively%5D%20is%20good.%20Hopefully%2C%20this%20nomination%20fuels%20any%20independent%20artist%20out%20there%20to%20have%20a%20great%20and%20enriching%20creative%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMusic%20permeating%20through%20the%20walls%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarijashree%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%2C%20a%20master%20flautist%2C%20and%20my%20mother%2C%20T%20V%20Rama%2C%20an%20accomplished%20vocalist%2C%20were%20my%20first%20gurus.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20everything%20started%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20memories%20as%20a%20toddler%20are%20few%2C%20but%20they%20come%20back%20to%20her%20in%20flashes.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20vividly%20remember%20sitting%20through%20%3Cem%3EAppa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20(father)%20flute%20lessons%20that%20he%20would%20give%20to%20students%20at%20home%20(he%20still%20avidly%20teaches%20to%20this%20day).%20Just%20being%20inside%20the%20house%2C%20I%20remember%20how%20the%20sound%20of%20my%20father%20playing%20the%20flute%20used%20to%20permeate%20the%20walls%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varijashree%20is%20a%20grammy-nominated%20artist%20%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778-768x960.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778-150x188.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778.jpg%201080w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382687%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVarijashree%20Venugopal%20won%20a%20Grammy%20nomination%20earlier%20this%20year%20(Image%20courtesy%20Yeashu%20Yuraj)%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Varijashree%E2%80%99s%20parents%20took%20her%20to%20many%20Carnatic%20music%20concerts.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20also%20memories%20of%20attending%20weddings%2C%20and%20if%20my%20parents%20could%20not%20find%20me%2C%20it%20was%20understood%20that%20I%20was%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20the%20musicians%20playing%20the%20%3Cem%3ENadaswaram%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20double-reed%20wind%20instrument%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EThavil%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20barrel-shaped%20drum%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20remembers%20observing%20other%20musicians%20who%20were%20friends%20of%20her%20father%E2%80%99s.%20She%20would%20listen%2C%20watch%2C%20and%20observe%20how%20they%20not%20only%20performed%20but%20also%20learnt%2C%20practised%2C%20and%20perceived%20art.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20I%20did%20not%20understand%20much%20as%20a%20child%2C%20it%20all%20started%20to%20make%20sense%20when%20I%20began%20to%20grasp%20the%20finer%20nuances%20of%20music%3B%20these%20were%20very%20valuable%20memories%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20child%20prodigy%20comes%20to%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20incredible%20talent%20and%20having%20learnt%20all%20the%20fundamentals%20from%20her%20first%20gurus%2C%20Varijashree%E2%80%99s%20parents%20felt%20it%20was%20best%20to%20enrol%20her%20in%20more%20formal%20and%20focused%20lessons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%20four%2C%20she%20began%20formal%20training%20in%20Carnatic%20vocals%20under%20Vidhushi%20(a%20title%20for%20a%20female%20Carnatic%20classical%20musician)%20H%20Geetha.%20Varijashree%20was%20seven%20when%20she%20gave%20her%20first%20full-fledged%20Carnatic%20vocal%20performance%20at%20the%20Bangalore%20Gayana%20Samaja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20learning%20under%20her%20tutelage%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20I%20also%20learned%20some%20rare%20and%20exclusive%20compositions%20from%20Vidhushi%20Vasantha%20Srinivasan%20and%20Vidwan%20(a%20title%20for%20a%20male%20Carnatic%20musician)%20D%20S%20Srivatsa.%20However%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20my%20formal%20training%20occurred%20under%20Gaanakalanidhi%20Vidwan%20Salem%20P%20Sundaresan.%20I%20was%20fortunate%20to%20have%20him%20as%20my%20guru.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20came%20under%20his%20tutelage%2C%20he%20was%2080%20years%20old.%20An%20ex-bank%20manager%2C%20my%20guru%20was%20an%20encyclopaedia%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F253401%2Fkerala-peruvemba-mridangam-carnatic-music-instrument-kasumani-indian-musicians-family-legacy-history-tradition-culture-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarnatic%20music%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20spent%2015%20years%20of%20intense%20training%20under%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varijashree%20Venugopal%3A%20From%20a%20child%20prodigy%20to%20a%20Grammy%20nomination.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVarijashree%20Venugopal%3A%20From%20a%20child%20prodigy%20to%20a%20Grammy%20nomination.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20picking%20up%20the%20flute%20and%20learning%20how%20to%20play%20it%20formally%20was%20not%20planned.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20it%20just%20happened%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20a%20pleasant%2C%20yet%20accidental%20surprise%20to%20me%20and%20to%20my%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20curious%20about%20the%20instrument%2C%20and%20I%20would%20dabble%20and%20experiment%20with%20it%20in%20between%20my%20ninth%20and%20tenth%20years%20of%20formal%20training.%20Luckily%2C%20I%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20produce%20a%20sound%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20most%20difficult%20part%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20bamboo%20flute.%20I%20had%20also%20secretly%20tried%20learning%20some%20things%20that%20my%20father%20was%20already%20teaching%20other%20students.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20told%20him%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20show%20him%20how%20I%20played%20a%20certain%20composition%20on%20the%20flute.%20To%20his%20surprise%2C%20I%20played%20something%20that%20was%20more%20proficient%20than%20he%20had%20expected.%20So%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20train%20me%20formally.%20Soon%2C%20I%20started%20accompanying%20him%20in%20his%20concerts%2C%20and%20later%20on%2C%20I%20began%20performing%20in%20my%20own%20solo%20flute%20concerts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20playing%20in%20recording%20sessions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarijashree%20was%20just%20about%2014%20years%20old%20when%20she%20began%20accompanying%20her%20father!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoing%20beyond%20the%20world%20of%20Carnatic%20music%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20she%20grew%20up%20in%20an%20environment%20steeped%20in%20the%20essence%20of%20Carnatic%20music%2C%20her%20parents%20also%20exposed%20her%20to%20a%20world%20beyond%20it%20through%20audio%20cassette%20tapes.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20used%20to%20play%20audio%20cassettes%20every%20day.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20Carnatic%20music%3B%20they%20also%20played%20Hindustani%20music%20and%20light%20classical%20forms%20like%20%3Cem%3EBhajans%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EAbhang%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fusion%20acts%20like%20Shakti%2C%20John%20McLaughlin%2C%20and%20L%20Shankar.%20These%20were%20some%20of%20the%20initial%20influences%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%2C%20however%2C%20changed%20everything.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20she%20discovered%20a%20wealth%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F54054%2Fjazz-india-1920-bombay-louis-banks-bollywood-bands%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejazz%20music%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20particularly%20artists%20like%20Chick%20Corea%2C%20Miles%20Davis%2C%20John%20Coltrane%2C%20and%20Bobby%20McFerrin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20initially%20drawn%20more%20to%20jazz%20and%20its%20associated%20forms%20because%20of%20the%20improvisational%20space%20it%20offers.%20That%20resonated%20with%20me%20because%20Indian%20classical%20music%20is%20also%20highly%20improvisational%20while%20being%20structured.%20What%20fascinated%20me%20was%20that%20jazz%20improvisations%20are%20not%20confined%20to%20a%20raga%3B%20they%20move%20through%20changing%20tonalities%20and%20explore%20various%20directions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20something%20I%20had%20never%20heard%20before%2C%20and%20it%20prompted%20me%20to%20try%20to%20sing%20those%20elements.%20My%20only%20goal%20was%20to%20see%20if%20I%20could%20emulate%20what%20a%20jazz%20instrumentalist%20or%20vocalist%20was%20performing%2C%20including%20scatting.%20I%20wanted%20to%20experiment%20with%20moving%20my%20vocal%20techniques%20in%20this%20new%20format%2C%20and%20that%20led%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%20and%20experimentation%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20this%20day.%20Every%20new%20piece%20I%20work%20on%20remains%20an%20extension%20of%20that%20exercise%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDBvVEdbMGsZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDBvVEdbMGsZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDBvVEdbMGsZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Varijashree%20Venugopal%20(%40varijashree)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarnatic%20music%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20intricately%20designed%20forms%20of%20classical%20music.%20Training%20in%20and%20practising%20this%20style%20is%20why%20Varijashree%20believes%20she%20can%20appreciate%2C%20understand%2C%20and%20approach%20other%20genres%20of%20music.%20However%2C%20listening%20to%20and%20being%20exposed%20to%20different%20genres%20has%20broadened%20her%20perspective%20and%20expanded%20her%20understanding%20of%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20listening%20to%20other%20forms%20has%20amplified%20my%20enjoyment%20of%20Carnatic%20music%20and%20influenced%20how%20I%20present%20a%20Carnatic%20%3Cem%3EKacheri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(concert).%20Applying%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20classical%20Carnatic%20music%20in%20a%20global%20context%20has%20enabled%20me%20to%20transcribe%20a%20jazz%20solo%20into%20Indian%20notation%20and%20then%20improvise%20on%20it%20while%20incorporating%20those%20fundamentals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECollaborating%20with%20Jacob%20Collier%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2012%20years%2C%20Varijashree%20has%20worked%20with%20a%20series%20of%20legendary%20Jazz%20artists%20from%20the%20West%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Victor%20Wooten%20and%20Bobby%20McFerrin.%20Working%20in%20these%20spaces%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20tap%20into%20a%20network%20of%20similarly%20talented%20and%20renowned%20artists.%20It%20is%20through%20this%20network%20stretching%20across%20continents%20that%20Jacob%20and%20Varijashree%20got%20to%20know%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20a%20fan%20of%20his%20work.%20Similarly%2C%20one%20of%20my%20videos%20may%20have%20appeared%20on%20his%20radar%2C%20following%20which%20he%20figured%20out%20that%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20common%20friends.%20We%20used%20to%20keep%20in%20touch%20now%20and%20then%20on%20Instagram.%20One%20day%2C%20however%2C%20he%20wrote%20to%20me%20saying%20that%20he%20was%20recording%20the%20fourth%20volume%20of%20Djesse%20(Djesse%20Vol.%204%20album)%20and%20that%20there%20was%20this%20song%20where%20he%20was%20imagining%20my%20voice%20that%20he%20thought%20would%20add%20perfectly%20well%20into%20the%20blend%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_466221808_527686340145671_4005691837502396191_n_1080-1732544376.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varijashree%20with%20Jacob%20Collier%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_466221808_527686340145671_4005691837502396191_n_1080-1732544376.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_466221808_527686340145671_4005691837502396191_n_1080-1732544376-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_466221808_527686340145671_4005691837502396191_n_1080-1732544376-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_466221808_527686340145671_4005691837502396191_n_1080-1732544376-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_466221808_527686340145671_4005691837502396191_n_1080-1732544376-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382701%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVarijashree%20with%20Jacob%20Collier%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20a%20fan%20of%20his%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_466090024_107071840