Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20vets%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20introduced%20%E2%80%98Exam%20D%20Pro%E2%80%99%2C%20designed%20to%20help%20busy%20professionals%20on%20the%20go.%20It%20enables%20instant%20tracking%20of%20multiple%20vitals%20and%20provides%20quicker%20access%20to%20data%20during%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20tracks%20multiple%20metrics%20that%20vets%20are%20trained%20to%20interpret%2C%20such%20as%20murmur%20identification%20and%20grading%20for%20early%20detection%20of%20heart%20conditions%2C%20lung%20abnormalities%2C%20and%20insights%20into%20issues%20like%20COPD%2C%20asthma%2C%20and%20wheezing%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vani.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20provides%20trend%20analytics%2C%20continuous%20care%20insights%20for%20proactive%20health%20monitoring%2C%20and%20ECG%20readings%20to%20detect%20heart%20irregularities.%E2%80%9D%20Exam%20D%20Pro%20was%20launched%20alongside%20Exam%20D%20in%20early%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20further%2C%20they%20also%20brought%20on%20board%20medical%20professionals%20and%20developed%20a%20digitised%20system%20called%20PAWS%20(Pets%20Administration%20and%20Workflow%20System)%20for%20pet%20parents%20and%20veterinary%20clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%20system%2C%20pet%20parents%20can%20directly%20connect%20with%20their%20vets.%20Vani%20said%20in%20a%20past%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20device%2C%20there%20is%20an%20app%20that%20connects%20with%20the%20SaaS%20solution%20that%20the%20vet%20has.%20He%20has%20an%20app%20version%2C%20so%20he%20has%20data%20at%20his%20fingertips.%20All%20the%20data%20goes%20in%20a%20click%20of%20a%20button%20to%20the%20vet.%20They%20can%20set%20up%20calls%20online%20or%20offline.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDCZF9okIh6V%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Free